		<descript>
			<langdata>eng</langdata>
			<abstract>
New York Commuter Rail Lines, 2025 is a line theme representing the Long Island Rail Road and Metro-North Railroad lines as of 2025. This dataset was derived from the New York State data repository (at https://data.ny.gov/Transportation/MTA-Rail-Branches-Map/jbqr-kiev) in March 2026. Columbia Libraries staff has provided the data in the geopackage format in state plane coordinates.
			</abstract>
